Sinovel Shares Surge After Report on First 6-Megawatt Turbine

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-05-31T02:54:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/sinovel-shares-surge-after-report-on-first-6-megawatt-turbine.html
Sinovel Wind Group Co., the world’s
second-biggest wind-turbine maker, jumped the most since listing
after Xinhua News Agency reported that the company had rolled
out  China ’s first 6-megawatt wind turbine.  The shares rose 8.8 percent to 60.99 yuan as of 10:30 a.m.
in  Shanghai , heading for its biggest gain since the stock
started trading in January.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  